# Performance Rules

- Avoid N+1 queries; eager load intentionally.
- Keep expensive computations off synchronous request path when possible.
- Use caching with clear invalidation strategy for read-heavy paths.
- Paginate large datasets and bound untrusted query parameters.
- Measure before/after for major performance-sensitive changes.
